query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(c cs dd cd1) NoNestLoop(c cd1 cs dd ca) NoMergeJoin(c ca cd1 cs dd i cd2) */ select i.i_item_id,
ca.ca_country,
ca.ca_state,
ca.ca_county,
avg(cs.cs_quantity::numeric(12, 2)) AS agg1,
avg(cs.cs_list_price::numeric(12, 2)) AS agg2,
avg(cs.cs_coupon_amt::numeric(12, 2)) AS agg3,
avg(cs.cs_sales_price::numeric(12, 2)) AS agg4,
avg(cs.cs_net_profit::numeric(12, 2)) AS agg5,
avg(c.c_birth_year::numeric(12, 2)) AS agg6,
avg(cd1.cd_dep_count::numeric(12, 2)) AS agg7
from date_dim AS dd
inner join catalog_sales AS cs
on cs.cs_sold_date_sk = dd.d_date_sk AND dd.d_year = 2001
inner join customer AS c
on cs.cs_bill_customer_sk = c.c_customer_sk AND c.c_birth_month IN (9,
5,
12,
4,
1,
10)
inner join customer_demographics AS cd1
on cs.cs_bill_cdemo_sk = cd1.cd_demo_sk AND cd1.cd_gender = 'M' AND cd1.cd_education_status = 'College'
inner join customer_address AS ca
on c.c_current_addr_sk = ca.ca_address_sk AND ca.ca_state IN ('ND',
'WI',
'AL',
'NC',
'OK',
'MS',
'TN')
inner join item AS i
on cs.cs_item_sk = i.i_item_sk
inner join customer_demographics AS cd2
on c.c_current_cdemo_sk = cd2.cd_demo_sk group by rollup(i.i_item_id, ca.ca_country, ca.ca_state, ca.ca_county) order by ca.ca_country, ca.ca_state, ca.ca_county, i.i_item_id LIMIT 100;
